# TrendLab Project Rules

- Follow `AGENTS.md` first.
- Read `docs/Status.md` and `docs/Plan.md` before non-trivial changes.
- Respect the milestone order: truthful lab, then CLI, then TUI shell.
- Keep Rust workspace boundaries clean.
- Keep diffs scoped to the active milestone.
- Keep default validation deterministic and network-free.
- Update `docs/Status.md` when milestone-level work changes repo state.
